OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FBright spells and a few showers from
OL,7,Fthe west on Thursday. A further rain
OL,8,Fband pushes northeast on Friday.
OL,9,FBright spells and showers again on
OL,10,FSaturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
